Release Date: 14 August 2025 

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji.

snippet.title: Bhide ने फेंका Dr. Hathi के ऊपर बाल्टी भरके पानी | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Scenes
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Bhide is out in his living room, relaxing as he reads the newspaper. But soon his peace gets disrupted by Tapu Sena's constant noise and he tells them to keep quiet! Find out more by watching the episode.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 597
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2025  #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta #comedyscene #tmkocbestcomedy 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Comedy Scenes' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cS8wi0cuF6h1ZN4wQuXjH2m

snippet.title: Detective Ujjwalan - Official Trailer | Dhyan Sreenivasan | Indraneel Gopeekrishnan, Rahul G | Rzee
snippet.description:
For more latest songs & videos, subscribe 👉 https://bit.ly/Saregama_Malayalam

Presenting the official trailer of Detective Ujjwalan, starring Dhyan Sreenivasan in the titular role. Produced by Sophia Paul under the banner of Weekend Blockbusters and directed by Indraneel Gopeekrishnan & Rahul G, this film marks the second installment of the Weekend Cinematic Universe.

Cast: Dhyan Sreenivasan, Siju Wilson, Rony David Raj, Kottayam Nazeer, Seema G Nair, Ameen, Nihal Nizam, Nibraz Noushad, Shahubas, Kalabhavan Navas, Nirmal Palazhi

Trailer Music Credits:

Composed and Produced by Sibi Mathew Alex
Co-produced and Guitars by Durwin D’souza
Vocals by Sibi Mathew Alex
Lyrics by Ann Lilly Jose
Mixed and Mastered by Abin Paul

Crew:
Written & Directed by: Indraneel Gopeekrishnan - Rahul G  
Produced by: Sophia Paul  
Executive Producer: Manuel Cruz Darwin

snippet.title: Jurassic World Rebirth | Official Trailer 2
snippet.description:
The worst of the worst dinosaurs were left here. Watch the final trailer for Jurassic World Rebirth and get tickets now.
-----
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@jurassicworld
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/jurassicworld
X: https://twitter.com/jurassicworld
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/jurassicworld
Official Site: https://www.jurassicworld.com/

A new era is born. This summer, three years after the Jurassic World trilogy concluded with each film surpassing $1 billion at the global box office, the enduring Jurassic series evolves in an ingenious new direction with Jurassic World Rebirth. 

Anchored by iconic action superstar Scarlett Johansson, Emmy and SAG nominee Jonathan Bailey and two-time Oscar® winner Mahershala Ali, this action-packed new chapter sees an extraction team race to the most dangerous place on Earth, an island research facility for the original Jurassic Park, inhabited by the worst of the worst that were left behind. 

Also starring acclaimed international stars Rupert Friend and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo, the film is directed by dynamic visualist Gareth Edwards (Rogue One: A Star Wars Story) from a script by original Jurassic Park screenwriter David Koepp. 

Five years after the events of Jurassic World Dominion, the planet’s ecology has proven largely inhospitable to dinosaurs. Those remaining exist in isolated equatorial environments with climates resembling the one in which they once thrived. The three most colossal creatures across land, sea and air within that tropical biosphere hold, in their DNA, the key to a drug that will bring miraculous life-saving benefits to humankind.

Academy Award® nominee Johansson plays skilled covert operations expert Zora Bennett, contracted to lead a skilled team on a top-secret mission to secure the genetic material. When Zora’s operation intersects with a civilian family whose boating expedition was capsized by marauding aquatic dinos, they all find themselves stranded on a forbidden island that had once housed an undisclosed research facility for Jurassic Park. There, in a terrain populated by dinosaurs of vastly different species, they come face-to-face with a sinister, shocking discovery that has been hidden from the world for decades. 

Ali is Duncan Kincaid, Zora’s most trusted team member; Critics Choice and Olivier Award winner Jonathan Bailey (Wicked, Bridgerton) plays paleontologist Dr. Henry Loomis; Emmy nominee Rupert Friend (Homeland, Obi-Wan Kenobi) appears as Big Pharma representative Martin Krebs and Manuel Garcia-Rulfo (The Lincoln Lawyer, Murder on the Orient Express) plays Reuben Delgado, the father of the shipwrecked civilian family. 

The cast includes Luna Blaise (Manifest), David Iacono (The Summer I Turned Pretty) and Audrina Miranda (Lopez vs. Lopez) as Reuben’s family. The film also features, as members of Zora and Krebs’ crews, Philippine Velge (Station Eleven), Bechir Sylvain (BMF) and Ed Skrein (Deadpool). 
 
Jurassic World Rebirth is directed by BAFTA winner Edwards from a script by Koepp (War of the Worlds), based on characters created by Michael Crichton. The film is produced by Oscar® nominee Frank Marshall and Patrick Crowley, both longtime Jurassic franchise producers and of last summer’s blockbuster, Twisters. The film is executive produced by Steven Spielberg, Denis L. Stewart and Jim Spencer.

Roshan Singh Sodhi has been absolutely drunk and he is not being allowed back in his house. He tries absolutely crazy things to get back in his house. Will they work? How does excessive consumption of alcohol be a problem for him? Find out in this episode.

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTXtajBo1G2UEa_wE8BVSU7

snippet.title: কৃষ্ণনগরে বন্যা | Gopal Bhar | Episode - 1154
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

The people of Krishnanagar are worried as continuous rainfall leads to flooding in the kingdom. Will Gopal come up with a solution in time?

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By: Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By: Hansa Mondal
Original language: Bengali
Episode No: 1154

#GopalBhar #sonyaath #গোপালভর 

About Gopal Bhar:
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him as a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Click to watch all the episodes of Gopal Bhar -
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcASj1d8U8PvhnbuO58CfvdkLU

snippet.description:
From the bustling kitchens of culinary innovation to the humble hearths of traditional Tamil Nadu, Chef Deena, a connoisseur of authentic flavors, recently found himself captivated. He wasn't just observing; he was witnessing a culinary legacy unfold as the esteemed Mrs. Kavithamani of Thothathu Virundhu, Erode, graciously demonstrated the secrets behind her renowned Pottu Kadalai Kuzhambu.

Thottathu Virunthu,
Mr. Sivanantham & Mrs. Kavithamani Sivanantham
Contact :  9842742126  /9842651113
Thindal - Villarasampatty Rd, near Sree Lakshmi Duraisamy Mahal, 
Villarasampatti, Erode, Tamil Nadu 638012 

Pottu Kadalai Kuzhambu
Fried Gram - 1 Cup 
Tomato - 10 Nos.
Onion - 6 Nos.
Green Chilli - 10 Nos. 
Mustard - For Tempering 
Salt - To Taste
Turmeric Powder - 1/2 Tsp 
Garam Masala - 1/4 Tsp 
Sambar Powder - 1 & 1/2 Tsp 
Groundnut Oil - For Tempering

_______________
Hello!!  My Name is chef Deena from the popular Adupangarai show in Jaya TV Viewers must have seen me in Zee Tamil shows as well.  My Culinary journey as a trainee to become an Executive Chef is incredible. My experience in the culinary field is for more than fifteen years and my USP is Indian cooking !! Apart from being a TV cookery host, my experience lies mainly with being employed in some of the major star hotels across the country especially the Marriott group.

     Chef Deena Cooks is my English Youtube Channel! Practical, simple recipes are my forte and using minimal easily available ingredients is my hallmark. Rudiments of cooking and baking are taught from scratch and any amateur cook can learn to make exciting dishes by watching my channel!  Also, Cooking traditional foods, Easy cooking Recipes, Healthy Snacks, Indian curries, gravies, Baking and Millions of other homemade treats.

Episode 4401: Gokuldham Members Ko Laga Shock
--------------------------------------------------------
The Gokuldham residents panic after an electric shock incident and rush to turn off the main switch, only to realize the keys are missing. With no other option, they call Bhide for help.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: TRUMP v2.0 | Standup Comedy by Rahul Dua | 2025
snippet.description:
Move over IPL 2.0, here is Trump 2.0.
I travelled to USA and Canada in Feb-Mar 2025 for my standup comedy tour with my new special (btw, India tour is on and I am coming to Australia and New Zealand, so you can get the tickets here: https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour).
This video has jokes about my time and my observations there, based on true events: USA vs Canada, Trump and Elon Musk, missed flights, the tip culture and more. Wrote, rehearsed and recorded all within a month of travel, so pls give it a watch and let me know you favourite joke in the comments below. 
Pls drop a like, it really helps the video. and share it with your friends and family members who are in USA or are planning to visit. 

#standupcomedy #trump #usavscanada 

Shot at The Regent Theatre, Boston, MA on 29th March 2025
Shot by: Prathmesh Mohite (@shutterversebypm)

localized.title: TRUMP v2.0 | Standup Comedy by Rahul Dua | 2025
localized.description:
Move over IPL 2.0, here is Trump 2.0.
I travelled to USA and Canada in Feb-Mar 2025 for my standup comedy tour with my new special (btw, India tour is on and I am coming to Australia and New Zealand, so you can get the tickets here: https://linktr.ee/therahulduatour).
This video has jokes about my time and my observations there, based on true events: USA vs Canada, Trump and Elon Musk, missed flights, the tip culture and more. Wrote, rehearsed and recorded all within a month of travel, so pls give it a watch and let me know you favourite joke in the comments below. 
Pls drop a like, it really helps the video. and share it with your friends and family members who are in USA or are planning to visit. 

#standupcomedy #trump #usavscanada 

Shot at The Regent Theatre, Boston, MA on 29th March 2025
Shot by: Prathmesh Mohite (@shutterversebypm)
Edited by: Gaurav Bhatt (@gauravbhatt101)

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: नौकरी गयी तेल लेने, ज्यादा बक-बक की, तो यही पटक कर रख दूंगा - Sanjay Kapoor - Johnny Lever Comedy
snippet.description:
Watch Comedy Scene Of Kader Khan and Johnny Lever From Movie " Sirf Tum "

Get ready for a hilarious rollercoaster with Sirf Tum! Watch as Kader Khan's comic genius and Johnny Lever's impeccable timing combine with Sanjay Kapoor's charm in this laugh-out-loud comedy. From side-splitting mishaps to laughable misunderstandings, this film is packed with moments that will keep you in splits. Whether it’s Kader Khan's comic wisdom or Johnny Lever's laugh-inducing antics, Sirf Tum guarantees endless fun and laughter!"

"Sirf Tum में हंसी की बौछार का आनंद लें! देखिए कैसे कादर खान की हास्य प्रतिभा और जॉनी लीवर का अद्वितीय समय साथ मिलकर संजय कपूर के आकर्षण के साथ हंसते-हंसते लोटपोट कर देते हैं। मजेदार गड़बड़ियों से लेकर हंसी-मजाक की भरपूर स्थिति तक, इस फिल्म में ऐसे पल भरे पड़े हैं जो आपको हंसते-हंसते गिरा देंगे। चाहे कादर खान की हास्य बुद्धिमत्ता हो या जॉनी लीवर की हंसी-मजाक की हरकतें, Sirf Tum हंसी और आनंद की गारंटी है!"

Movie: Sirf Tum (1999)

Cast: Kader Khan, Johnny Lever, Sanjay Kapoor, Priya Gill, Sushmita Sen, Jackie Shroff, Mohnish Behl

Music: Nadeem-Shravan

Director: Agathiyan

Producer: Boney Kapoor

#SirfTum #ComedyGold #kaderkhan #johnnylever  #KaderKhanMagic #JohnnyLeverFun #SanjayKapoorLaughs #BollywoodComedy #HilariousMoments #LaughOutLoud #hasterahocomedy

snippet.title: Google I/O 2025 keynote in 32 minutes
snippet.description:
Google just wrapped up its big keynote at I/O 2025. As expected, it was full of AI-related announcements, ranging from updates across Google’s image and video generation models to new features in Search and Gmail. We got a look at Project Astra’s latest prototype that will complete tasks on your behalf, Gemini 2.5 Pro updates, a new AI filmmaking app called Flow, Project Starline is now Google Beam. Plus, a look at Xreal’s new Project Aura prototype. Here’s everything you missed.

0:26 Google Beam/Project Starline

2:34 Project Mariner

snippet.title: Raavan - Full Movie 4K - Abhishek Bachchan, Vikram, Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Govinda, Ravi Kishan
snippet.description:
First Time On Youtube - Raavan Full Movie 4K  ab pehli baar YouTube par – woh bhi 4K mein!
Mani Ratnam ki iss epic film mein hai emotion, thrill aur ek aisa jungle jahan sach aur jhooth ka fark mushkil ho jaata hai. Raavan 👹 Full Movie 4K 🔥 Abhishek Bachchan, Vikram, Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Govinda, Ravi Kishan

एक डाकू एक अधिकारी की पत्नी का अपहरण कर लेता है, उससे प्यार करने लगता है और उसे जाने देता है, लेकिन बाद में उसे एहसास होता है कि वह उससे प्यार करती है। यह एहसास होने पर, उसका अपना पति डाकू तक पहुँचने के लिए उसे बलि का बकरा बनाता है।

निर्देशक - मणिरत्नम
कहानी और पटकथा - मणिरत्नम
संवाद - विजय कृष्ण आचार्य
निर्माता - मणिरत्नम, शारदा त्रिलोक
अभिनीत - अभिषेक बच्चन, विक्रम, ऐश्वर्या राय बच्चन, गोविंदा, निखिल द्विवेदी, रवि किशन, प्रियमणि
छायाकार - संतोष सिवन, वी. मणिकंदन
संपादक - ए. श्रीकर प्रसाद
संगीत - ए. आर. रहमान

#abhishekbachchan #aishwarya #vikram #govinda #ravikishan #priyamani #ravan #mainratnam #bollywoodmovie #firsttimeonyoutube 

A bandit kidnaps an officer's wife, falls in love with her and lets her go, only to realise that she is in love with him. Realising this, her own husband uses her as a scapegoat to reach the bandit.

Director - Mani Ratnam
Story & Screenplay - Mani Ratnam
Dialogues - Vijay Krishna Acharya
Producer - Mani Ratnam, Sharada Trilok
Starring - Abhishek Bachchan, Vikram, Aishwarya Rai Bachchan, Govinda, Nikhil Dwivedi, Ravi Kishan, Priyamani
Cinematographer - Santosh Sivan, V. Manikandan
Editor - A. Sreekar Prasad
Music - A. R. Rahman

snippet.title: Apple’s iPhone 17 Series Will Be Totally Different  !
snippet.description:
kya satra.....khatra hoga?

🔥 Subscribe for Tabahi Videos

iPhone 17 Series Launch is one of the most anticipated tech events of 2025! Apple is set to unveil the next generation of iPhones this September, featuring the all-new iPhone 17, iPhone 17 Plus, iPhone 17 Pro, and the ultra-slim iPhone 17 Air. With major design overhauls, performance upgrades, and deeper Apple Intelligence integration, the iPhone 17 lineup promises to redefine what a smartphone can do.

Expected upgrades include the A18 and A18 Pro chips, 120Hz OLED displays across all models, under-display Face ID, and AI-enhanced cameras. The iPhone 17 Pro models may introduce a titanium frame 2.0, thinner bezels, and improved periscope telephoto lens, while the iPhone 17 Air will debut as the thinnest and lightest iPhone ever — designed for those who want power in a minimal form.

Apple will likely reveal iOS 19 innovations alongside the launch, with deep integrations of Siri AI, Genmoji, Live Transcribe, Smart Recap, and Private Compute Cloud features.

📆 Launch Date (Expected): September 10, 2025
📱 Models Expected: iPhone 17, iPhone 17 Plus, iPhone 17 Pro, iPhone 17 Pro Max, iPhone 17 Air
💸 India Price Range: ₹79,900 – ₹1,59,900
🛒 Availability: Apple India, Flipkart, Amazon, Reliance Digital
🔥 Pre-order Offers: Bank discounts, trade-in bonuses, and exclusive AppleCare+ bundles

If you’re searching for iPhone 17 launch event time, iPhone 17 Air specs, or comparisons like iPhone 17 Pro vs iPhone 16 Pro, this breakdown covers everything you need to know before the big Apple Event in 2025!

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. 

Are you ready for the challenge?

#GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame

Watch the FULL MOVIE of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSk2_rPKNCDcjNAA8vaDN-E&si=rC5AotwLD2r3MHna

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

snippet.description:
My favourite stories and my favourite part of my stand up special "Professor of Tomfoolery".

I have never been this personal with my stand up shows before so it felt amazing to open up and share stories about my parents and my childhood.

Hope you enjoy this clip and share it with your family and friends!

PS: I survived, don't worry.

I have never been this personal with my stand up shows before so it felt amazing to open up and share stories about my parents and my childhood.

Hope you enjoy this clip and share it with your family and friends!

PS: I survived, don't worry.

snippet.title: 2025 CBSE PAPER REVALUATION PROCESS | WHAT CAN BE FIXED? | A MUST-WATCH FOR EVERY STUDENT
snippet.description:
📢 2025 CBSE Paper Revaluation Process – What’s Wrong & What Needs to Change!
Is the CBSE revaluation process really fair? In this video, we break down the major flaws and limitations of the CBSE revaluation system in 2025 and discuss what changes are urgently needed.

🛑 If you feel your marks were unfairly deducted, this video is for you.

🎯 What we cover:
 • Common issues students face during revaluation
 • Why many genuine mistakes still go unfixed
 • The difference between revaluation, verification, and photocopy – and how each has limitations
 • Stories of students who lost marks due to a broken system
 • What reforms are needed to make the process more transparent and student-friendly

📌 Whether you’re in Class 10 or Class 12, understanding these flaws can help you take better decisions and also raise your voice for a better evaluation process.

⚠️ Don’t blindly trust the system – know your rights and the truth behind the process.

🔔 Subscribe for more honest educational content, CBSE updates, and student support videos.

#CBSE2025 #CBSERevaluationFlaws #CBSEBoardExam #CBSEClass12 #CBSEClass10 #CBSEUnfairMarking #CBSEReforms #StudentVoice #CBSEResults

📢 2025 CBSE Paper Revaluation Process – What’s Wrong & What Needs to Change!
Is the CBSE revaluation process really fair? In this video, we break down the major flaws and limitations of the CBSE revaluation system in 2025 and discuss what changes are urgently needed.

🛑 If you feel your marks were unfairly deducted, this video is for you.

🎯 What we cover:
 • Common issues students face during revaluation
 • Why many genuine mistakes still go unfixed
 • The difference between revaluation, verification, and photocopy – and how each has limitations
 • Stories of students who lost marks due to a broken system
 • What reforms are needed to make the process more transparent and student-friendly

📌 Whether you’re in Class 10 or Class 12, understanding these flaws can help you take better decisions and also raise your voice for a better evaluation process.

⚠️ Don’t blindly trust the system – know your rights and the truth behind the process.

🔔 Subscribe for more honest educational content, CBSE updates, and student support videos.

#CBSE2025 #CBSERevaluationFlaws #CBSEBoardExam #CBSEClass12 #CBSEClass10 #CBSEUnfairMarking #CBSEReforms #StudentVoice #CBSEResults

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SAB

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Tu hi dass mainu ki mileya

Fer main ravaya khud nu

Ajj takk mull mera 
Samjh na aya khud nu

Tu hi dass mainu ki mileya

Tenu ehna chaun toh baad

snippet.description:
🔥Rapid Fire Class #4 | RRB NTPC Reasoning Class | विजयी भव: सीरीज | Group D, UPP, SSC GD, CGL etc.

🙏 विजयी भव: सीरीज में आपका स्वागत है!
इस सीरीज की पहली क्लास में हम करेंगे Reasoning के महत्वपूर्ण और बार-बार पूछे जाने वाले सवालों की Rapid Fire Practice — वो भी बिना समय गवाए, सीधे एग्जाम पैटर्न के अनुसार!

📌 इस क्लास में मिलेगा:
✅ 30+ हाई स्कोरिंग Reasoning प्रश्न
✅ शॉर्टकट ट्रिक्स व त्वरित समाधान
✅ RRB NTPC CBT 1 और CBT 2 दोनों के लिए उपयोगी
✅ फुल स्पीड + फुल Accuracy प्रैक्टिस

📌 Target Exam: RRB NTPC, GROUP D, ALP, UP POLICE, SSC GD, CGL, CHSL, MTS, ARMY AGNIVEER etc.

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Mango Season' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQ935YpRdVQM7FT1bx86o84

snippet.title: மரண பள்ளத்தாக்கில் கால் பதித்து விட்டோம் | Death Valley | Chapter 1
snippet.description:
Exploring Death Valley National Park – Chapter 1

Come with me on an epic one-day road trip from Las Vegas to Death Valley National Park, one of the hottest and most extreme places on Earth! ☀️🔥

We started our journey early from Las Vegas, stopped for a relaxing breakfast, and stumbled upon a charming antique street shop along the way. With desert vibes kicking in, we finally reached the Death Valley National Park sign—and the excitement was real!

After grabbing our park pass, our first stop was the iconic Zabriskie Point – a breathtaking view of golden badlands shaped over millions of years. From there, we explored the unique and otherworldly wonders of Death Valley:

🧭 Stops in this vlog:
 • Zabriskie Point – stunning views and badland formations.
 • Furnace Creek – the heart of the valley and home to historic sites.
 • Badwater Basin – the lowest point in North America at 282 feet below sea level!
 • Devil’s Golf Course – jagged salt flats you can hear cracking beneath your feet.
 • Artist’s Palette – colorful hills formed by oxidized minerals.
 • Shoshone Village – a peaceful desert town with natural springs and history.

In this vlog, I also share fascinating scientific facts, geological insights, and historical stories that reveal the true wonder of Death Valley.

We wrapped up the day by heading back to Las Vegas, with hearts full and cameras packed with memories!

🎥 Perfect for science lovers, nature explorers, and road trip fans!
